title: UCF Panel Calls for End to Relationship Violence (University of Central Florida)
text: ( Source : University of Central Florida ) As part of its annual observance of National Domestic Violence Awareness Month, UCF hosted a forum Wednesday, Oct. 7, to honor the lives of domestic-violence victims and promote healthy relationships.
